        "brief_summary": {
            "textblock": "The World Health Organization (WHO) has recently declared coronavirus disease 2019 (Covid-19)\n      a public health emergency of international concern. Impact of the pandemic of covid-19 on the\n      mental health of health care workers and general population would be affected."
        },
        "detailed_description": {
            "textblock": "Health care workers and general population will be included in the study. An online\n      questionnaire will be used to assess their knowledge and practices regarding covid-19 and its\n      impact on mental health. Mental health regarding anxiety, depression and obsessive compulsive\n      disorder will be assess through online Hamilton anxiety , Hamilton Depression questionnaires\n      and Yale-Brown Obsessive Compulsive Scale (Y-BOCS)."
        },
